Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?fix(events):=20filter-inner=20alignment=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E2=80=94=20max-width=201280px,=20margin=20auto,=20padding=200?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=2028px?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
